<plot>A young beggar is enrolled into medieval knight school at the behest of the principal, much to the disgust and embarrassment of certain underhanded plotters in the school, who would love to see the head deposed and replaced by one of their own. The beggar has a lot to learn about being a knight, but in return, he has a lot teach them about honour and integrity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?294638</url></doc>
